Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.00,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,现在还什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.75,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,还有点心时刻的法杖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.60,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.98,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,现在还不能放松  待会再吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:50.75,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,前面好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.12,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,能看见光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:54.55,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.03,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,蜜柑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.20,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:58.95,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,先停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.26,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,尾巴绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.86,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,你这家伙对我的尾巴好点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.89,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,不要随便接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.55,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,之前我就说过了吧  先好好观察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.06,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,观察？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.23,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,看到那个你有什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.49,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,蜜柑好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.29,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,错误  魔族死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.55,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,浓重的黑雾包裹在蜜柑周围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.00,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,那应该是保护蜜柑的力场的中心部分
